Greetings from the enchanting town of Anyue, Sichuan! 🏞️ After nearly a decade, I’ve returned to my roots, savoring the essence of my childhood memories and the embrace of loved ones. 🌟 One of the most treasured parts of this visit is reuniting with my resilient grandparents, who continue to toil and sow with unwavering dedication. Their unwavering spirit and determination inspire me beyond words, showcasing the strength that flows through the veins of our family.
❤️ As the sun sets over the horizon, I feel an overwhelming sense of gratitude and admiration for this little town that played a crucial role in shaping my identity. #Hometown #sichuan #GratefulHeart #FamilyBond #BackToMyRoots

Exclusive shopping day at @southcoastplaza ! 🤩The special holiday shopping and dining experience made me feel spoiled by the South Coast Plaza family. Since I moved to OC years ago, South Coast Plaza has been my go-to destination for gift shopping, delightful culinary experiences, or simply hanging out with friends. The atmosphere and hospitality have always made it a cherished spot. This year I received my first Access Pass as a Christmas present, and I’m eagerly anticipating the opportunity to elevate my experiences even further! Cheers to many more memorable moments at South Coast Plaza 🥂✨🥰
